Source.Name: scribus
Source.Description: Scribus is an Open Source program that brings professional page layout with a combination of press-ready output and new approaches to page design. Underneath a modern and user-friendly interface, Scribus supports professional publishing features, such as color separations, CMYK and spot colors, ICC color management, and versatile PDF creation.
